OL,3,CPatient jailed for threatening to
OL,4,Cshoot doctor at GP surgery
OL,6,FA man has been jailed after a series
OL,7,Fof aggressive outbursts, which saw him
OL,8,Fracially abuse and threaten to shoot a
OL,9,Fdoctor at his local GP surgery.
OL,11,FJermaine Jones used racist language
OL,12,Ftowards a GP at a surgery in Doncaster
OL,13,Ffollowing a medical appointment on 3
OL,14,FJanuary.
OL,16,FA few days later, Jones returned to
OL,17,Fthe same surgery to request more
OL,18,Fmedication.
