OL,3,CPatient jailed for threatening to
OL,4,Cshoot doctor at GP surgery
OL,6,FHowever, after being told he had been
OL,7,Fbarred due to his previous behaviour,
OL,8,FJones threatened to shoot the same
OL,9,Fdoctor he had racially abused.
OL,11,FThe 49-year-old also shouted at other
OL,12,Fstaff at a community hub in the city
OL,13,Fcentre just days later on 9 January.
OL,15,FJones targeted one worker and
OL,16,Fthreatened them by saying: "I hope you
OL,17,Fcatch Hep C. You know what I am
OL,18,Fcapable of with guns and knives."
