OL,6,FCCTV then captured Jones abusing and
OL,7,Fthreatening to assault staff at a nail
OL,8,Fsalon in Doncaster city centre before
OL,9,Fhis arrest on 12 January.
OL,11,FWhile in custody at College Road
OL,12,FPolice Station, Jones urinated and
OL,13,Fdefecated on the floor.
OL,15,FJones was later charged with multiple
OL,16,Fpublic order offences and criminal
OL,17,Fdamage.
