OL,3,CPatient jailed for threatening to
OL,4,Cshoot doctor at GP surgery
OL,6,FHe was jailed for 20 weeks by
OL,7,FDoncaster Magistrates' Court after
OL,8,Fpleading guilty to two counts of using
OL,9,Fthreatening or abusive behaviour to
OL,10,Fcause harassment, two counts of
OL,11,Fracially aggravated harassment and one
OL,12,Fof criminal damage.
OL,14,FPC Matt Hubbard, who was the officer
OL,15,Fin the case, said he was "pleased"
OL,16,FJones was behind bars.
