OL,3,CPatient jailed for threatening to
OL,4,Cshoot doctor at GP surgery
OL,6,F"Jones made vicious threats of
OL,7,Fviolence and used vile racist language
OL,8,Fto target workers across Doncaster who
OL,9,Fwere simply going about their day-to-
OL,10,Fday jobs," he said.
OL,12,F"No worker should have had to put up
OL,13,Fwith his disgusting behaviour and we
OL,14,Fare pleased he is behind bars so he
OL,15,Fcan no longer be a menace to the
OL,16,Fpeople of Doncaster."
